 112          //--------------------------------------------------
 113          // Description  : HDCP 2.2 Down Load Value in INT
 114          // Input Value  : usSubAddr == > start address, usLength == > key Length,
 115          //                pReadArray == > Key Array
 116          // Output Value : None
